05:09.643 --> 05:11.811
- Hey, where are those kids?
- Excuse me?

05:11.979 --> 05:14.230
- "Right behind you, Father."
- Right behind you.

05:14.398 --> 05:16.148
Right behind you, Father.

05:17.067 --> 05:20.695
