06:02.362 --> 06:05.281
Okay, in the very first
Pleasantville episode...

06:05.449 --> 06:09.160
whose window did Bud break when he was
playing with his father's golf clubs?

06:09.327 --> 06:10.619
Easy. Mr. Jenkins.

06:10.787 --> 06:13.164
What job did Mr. Jenkins have?

06:14.750 --> 06:16.375
Salesman.

06:16.585 --> 06:21.672
What did Bud and Mary Sue name the cat
they found in the gutter?

06:22.174 --> 06:23.215
Scout?

06:24.176 --> 06:25.384
Marmalade.

06:25.594 --> 06:28.137
All right, all right.

06:28.305 --> 06:30.056
Here's one.

06:30.223 --> 06:34.143
Why did their parents come home early
from their weekend at the lake?

06:37.230 --> 06:40.483
Because Bud didn't answer the phone,
and they were worried about him.

06:40.650 --> 06:44.153
Man, you're unbelievable.

06:44.321 --> 06:47.073
