When is it on?

06:48.325 --> 06:51.660
Marathon starts at 6:30.
Contest is tomorrow at noon.

06:52.996 --> 06:55.915
Thousand bucks, huh?
And it's on all night?

06:56.083 --> 06:59.460
Well, of course it is, Howard.
That's why they call it a marathon.

07:00.712 --> 07:03.672
